  "text": "### 6.2 Direct Debits  \nA direct debit is an authorization for a biller to withdraw money.  \n**Setup:**\n- Provide authorization (mandate) to biller\n- Specify maximum amount\n- Biller initiates withdrawals  \n**Protection (Direct Debit Guarantee):**\n- Refund within 10 business days if unauthorized\n- No questions asked\n- Full protection under Direct Debit Guarantee  \n**Cancellation:**\n- Request from bank (5 days notice usually)\n- Or contact biller directly  \n---",
